{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A lockdown during a crisis. You can't go anywhere. At least not until a portal to a magical land opens in your bedroom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weirdlands is an RPG inspired by classics like Final Fantasy, Earthbound, Undertale, etc., but it's also very much its own thing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can recruit or capture pretty much any enemy you fight. The stronger, unique spirits have their own personalities and storylines. They can absorb other spirits you capture, gaining their abilities. With combining spirits like that, you can find combinations that work best for you, and even some hidden combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is a proper point &amp; click inventory with proper point &amp; click items for solving proper point &amp; click puzzles, but since it is an RPG, you can solve most puzzles in different ways, often with brute force, just make sure your brawn stat is high enough.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After you finish the game (or by turning it on in the options), you can start a new game+, which dramatically changes both story and game mechanics, giving you a very different experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is a huge amount of lore to uncover, both through the story itself and by exploring and finding hidden hints about what is going on in the world(s).  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dramatic Changes In Your Second Playthrough (New Game +)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple Solutions to Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Optional Content and Bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Countless Secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Huge Amount of Spirits to Catch </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Works On Steam Deck</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548350/extras/customBanner4.png?t=1735740593\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Isekai Traveler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1548350/d81a2d272737eb971b2bb14ae403fc3f3a222fdd.jpg"},{"name":"Hunter Hunted","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1548350/28168e2e0a62b47e656bf7ec18d885c163f16fd1.jpg"},{"name":"Star Pupil","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1548350/ea1b1e19f4b263647c908c0b9fdf3be00c2ba52c.jpg"},{"name":"Do Your Own Research","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1548350/405a7d89af2dd23f0525629333de150d40c5f875.jpg"},{"name":"Objection!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1548350/e1ed6efefc7af59a2581282be56e5d0df6d27f80.jpg"},{"name":"Hostile Takeover","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1548350/f1336942534ab3cd6c797c65235b746dc09ea93f.jpg"},{"name":"Spirit Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1548350/362b666d2cd6857cbd0429933e73b3cceeda4b80.jpg"},{"name":"Sticker Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1548350/158bc1f8b5c0414b9acc37ee452a96ae6659d889.jpg"},{"name":"Friend Of The Emberflies","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1548350/90f6a54d3346a692ac60a297df3c61db1bac1d5c.jpg"},{"name":"Eye spy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1548350/124b6e51014f1ff20a33eff61dfae538447ce12e.jpg"}],"total":27},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1548350?t=1735740593","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548350/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1735740593","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st